name: Labyrinth 2
description:
“A labyrinth is a symbolic journey . . . but it is a map we can really walk on, blurring the difference between map and world.”
― Rebecca Solnit, Wanderlust: A History of Walking

I use my photography, math and photomanipulation to create this images based in my imagination. Using "Phi" the golden number I generate patterns that helps me to build the labyrinths
